'''Cecil Moller''' (wavutse 1967) ni umuyobozi na producr wa firime muri  [[Namibiya]].

== Ubuzima bwa Biografiya ==
Moller yavukiye muri Namibiya mu 1967 akaza muri Amerika kwiga ubuhanzi. <ref name="africultures" /> Ashishikajwe no kumenya ibintu bifatika, yabonye impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu itumanaho yakuye muri Ramapo College . <ref name="chapman">https://issuu.com/dodge/docs/gradbook</ref> Moller yakoraga nka injeniyeri yijwi, cinematografi numwanditsi wibikorwa byinshi mbere yo kuyobora firime ye. Yatangiye gukina filime yerekanwe bwa mbere na ''No Plot'' mu 1991. Nibwo bwa mbere muri firime nyinshi zakozwe mu myaka ya za 90.  Mu 2000, itegeko rya komisiyo ishinzwe amafilime ya Namibiya ryatowe kugirango rizamure abayobozi ba firime nka Moller. <ref name="NelmesSelbo2015">https://books.google.com/books?id=kGikCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA29</ref>

Mu 2001, Moller yakoze ubushakashatsi ku mibereho yindaya muri Walvis Bay zishingiye ku bikamyo byoherezwa mu bihe byagenwe muri filime ngufi yatsindiye ''Inzu y'urukundo'' . <ref>http://newsreel.org/video/HOUSE-OF-LOVE</ref> Yashakaga kumenya impamvu abo bagore, bamwe muri bo yari azi kuva ku ishuri, babaye abakora imibonano mpuzabitsina.  Kuva 2004 kugeza 2007, yabaye umuyobozi wa komisiyo ishinzwe amafilime ya Namibiya. <ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/200707060347.html</ref> Moller yavuze ko Namibia yabuze 50% byâ€™amafaranga ashobora guturuka ku bicuruzwa mpuzamahanga mpuzamahanga mu gihugu nka ''Generation Kill'' kubera kubura ibikorwa remezo. <ref>https://www.namibian.com.na/print.php?id=36564&type=2</ref>

Moller yakuye impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu bijyanye no gutunganya amashusho muri kaminuza ya Chapman mu 2010.  Yasohokanye na firime ngufi ''Marvin na Stevie n'Imana'' nyuma gato yo kurangiza amashuri. <ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/201101270269.html</ref> Mu 2016, Moller bareganwa umusaruro Perivi Katjavivi i 'S Ikiranga mbere film ''bitaboneka,'' gucukumbura nsanganyamatsiko ya post-cy'ubukoloni Namibia ndangamuntu no existentialism. <ref>https://www.screenafrica.com/2016/04/10/film/the-unseen-explores-notions-of-postcolonial-identity-and-existentialism/</ref> Yabonye igihembo cyiza cya Diregiteri wa Filime muri Namibian Film & Theatre Awards 2017. <ref>http://artscouncilnam.org/component/phocagallery/category/17-2017-nfta-the-show</ref>

